commit.message: Updated readme with instructions on how to run app.
Factored login pages to extendables and includables.
Added CSRF back in. Completed login screen.
Fixed login authentication, but without caching.
Added all server-end authentication to sign up.
All signup validations except final check.
Added local signup authentications. Organized signup process. Wrote AJAX requests, but untested.
Got rid of superfluous front-end elements and libraries. Fixed db to allow user authentication. Increased responsiveness while reducing clutter. Will add authentication and fix signup form next.
Added an about page and updated the links
